{"tid":1013864,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"應俄羅斯要求 谷歌移除七成黑名單網站","createTime":"2019-02-08T16:22:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-08T22:02:07.000Z","uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"15c64de31e78b58d15583e03423e617e80ed1ac8","tid":1013864,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T16:22:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2019/02/08/2055023_754fe008dba10c9ad397a02843babe09.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.hkej.com%2Fhkej%2Fimages%2F2019%2F02%2F08%2F2055023_754fe008dba10c9ad397a02843babe09.jpg&h=83438c76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 谷歌(Google)據報已開始對俄羅斯境內的搜索結果進行調整，並根據俄國政府要求，移除大約七成被政府通訊機構列入黑名單的網站。<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯傳媒報道，自2017年以來，俄羅斯聯邦通訊監管局(Roskomnadzor)一直要求谷歌移除被當局明令禁止的網站，其中涉及兒童色情、毒品和自殺等。<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯法律規定，自去年10月1日起，進入俄羅斯市場的搜尋引擎必須接受一份官方擬定的非法網站目錄，並在搜索結果中加以遮蔽。報道指出，由於谷歌並沒有積極採納該規定，去年11月被罰款7500美元(5.85萬港元)。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/international/article/2055023/%E6%87%89%E4%BF%84%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82+%E8%B0%B7%E6%AD%8C%E7%A7%BB%E9%99%A4%E4%B8%83%E6%88%90%E9%BB%91%E5%90%8D%E5%96%AE%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Finternational%2Farticle%2F2055023%2F%25E6%2587%2589%25E4%25BF%2584%25E8%25A6%2581%25E6%25B1%2582%2B%25E8%25B0%25B7%25E6%25AD%258C%25E7%25A7%25BB%25E9%2599%25A4%25E4%25B8%2583%25E6%2588%2590%25E9%25BB%2591%25E5%2590%258D%25E5%2596%25AE%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E7%25AB%2599&d=SInmTBH44R2CRaFL2yHJ1Phh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=88f29bbc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/international/article/2055023/%E6%87%89%E4%BF%84%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82+%E8%B0%B7%E6%AD%8C%E7%A7%BB%E9%99%A4%E4%B8%83%E6%88%90%E9%BB%91%E5%90%8D%E5%96%AE%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99</a>"},{"pid":"2ab1481e4d2585da7dce5801c11b7ff04d7183c1","tid":1013864,"uid":94828,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T16:25:42.000Z","msg":"7500美元咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2490d49295b3b424b0607b6de03ad74b90ab1eca","tid":1013864,"uid":141151,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"2ab1481e4d2585da7dce5801c11b7ff04d7183c1","tid":1013864,"uid":94828,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T16:25:42.000Z","msg":"7500美元咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T16:30:43.000Z","msg":"嚇到google即刻delete黑名單網站<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a5b2959ee5dbd5446d853dc40961e107ba7fed6","tid":1013864,"uid":220701,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2490d49295b3b424b0607b6de03ad74b90ab1eca","tid":1013864,"uid":141151,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"2ab1481e4d2585da7dce5801c11b7ff04d7183c1","tid":1013864,"uid":94828,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T16:25:42.000Z","msg":"7500美元咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T16:30:43.000Z","msg":"嚇到google即刻delete黑名單網站<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T22:02:07.000Z","msg":"google執梗了<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}